Description: OneDrive client for Linux with FUSE filesystem
 A Linux client for Microsoft OneDrive that mounts your cloud storage
 as a local filesystem using FUSE. Files are downloaded on-demand when
 accessed, and local changes are automatically synced to OneDrive.
 .
 The package includes:
  - onedrive-sync-daemon: Background service that mounts OneDrive as FUSE
  - onedrive-sync-ui: Graphical interface for COSMIC/Pop!_OS
  - onedrive-sync-applet: System tray indicator

